    "In addition, channel estimation is also critical to the performance of wireless communications.",
    "Consequently, parameter estimation has received much attention as a key task within ISAC.",
    "Although various model-based parameter estimation algorithms have been proposed, they often face the challenges of high complexity and poor performance in dynamic environments, hindering their practical application [217].",
    "Due to the great learning ability, fast inference, and satisfactory generalization, AI techniques have been widely used as low-complexity alternatives to the traditional ones for parameter estimation, especially when the environment is highly dynamic.",
